Team
Competitions
DARPA Subterranean Challenge 2019
As part of the winning CMU team, I performed initial experimentation on wireless mesh networking
for consistent communication among robots, access points and base station in mines and caves.
IEEE Signal Processing Cup 2017
We built a real-time beat tracking algorithm running on an embedded device reacting to a variety
of music signals. Check out our trippy visualizations here!.
IEEE Signal Processing Cup 2016
We developed a solution to extract power signal leaking into recorded audio signals and geolocate
the power grid where audio was recorded. We finished top 15 in the world!
